[13:06:31] Epic: Fix bd show performance in beads-parallel.sh
[13:06:31] Description: Optimize Beads queries to avoid 11-second delays per task.

## Problem
Each `bd show` call takes ~11 seconds. For 4 tasks = 44 seconds just fetching metadata.

## Solutions (pick one)
1. Cache Beads data in memory (fetch once, reuse)
2. Use `bd list --json` to fetch all tasks at once
3. Run bd show calls in parallel (xargs -P)

